Since 34 years that I separated from this woman, I saw her here in The SCOAN for the first time.

0:03:13.200,0:03:22.600
I never knew it could be possible.

0:03:22.600,0:03:28.920
Last Sunday, the man of God gave me a prophecy.

0:03:28.920,0:03:33.920
He said that I had married and re-married and that I've gotten three wives.

0:03:33.920,0:03:40.620
He then asked me where my wife was and I said I didn't have one because really, I have none.

0:03:40.620,0:03:50.740
I told him that if I married, they would run away as if I was the ugliest man in the world.

0:03:50.740,0:03:57.500
It all started when I wanted to get married.

0:03:57.500,0:04:08.620
I was not actually in love with my ex-wife; it was my mother's arrangement.

0:04:08.620,0:04:16.760
She said I was going to marry the lady.

0:04:16.760,0:04:29.160
I didn't know her but for me to respect my mother's decision, for me to make my mother happy,

0:04:29.160,0:04:30.320
I had to marry her.

