Actually, when I married her, we were going fine.

0:04:35.020,0:04:41.220
Things were going fine until I started making money.

0:04:41.220,0:04:47.620
I was into transport business and I started flourishing.

0:04:47.620,0:04:52.380
I bought trailers and that was where the trouble started.

0:04:52.380,0:04:58.360
I can remember, she used to go to the saloon and I got some experience there.

0:04:58.360,0:05:02.200
She would tell me to sign blank cheques for her

0:05:02.200,0:05:10.040
