0:05:10.040,0:05:14.200
I asked her where she got that idea from.

0:05:14.200,0:05:17.680
So, trouble started.

0:05:17.680,0:05:25.620
"Where did you get that, that I should sign a blank cheque for you to put any figure you like?"

0:05:25.620,0:05:27.640
I thought it was a joke.

0:05:27.640,0:05:39.120
The hatred increased; there was no month we were in peace.

0:05:39.120,0:05:41.480
To cut the story short...

0:05:41.480,0:05:46.020
I had two ships at Tin Can Wharf for clearing.

0:05:46.020,0:05:48.720
My wharf managers were already there.

0:05:48.720,0:05:53.300
I was carrying my briefcase to put inside my car to go to work.

0:05:53.300,0:05:58.420
All my sons were young then but they knew what happened.

0:05:58.420,0:06:12.160
As I was about to enter the car, she pulled my briefcase and said, "Don't you know that you daughter is sick

0:06:12.160,0:06:14.200
and you don’t care, you are going to work?"

0:06:14.200,0:06:20.540
I told her that I had introduced a doctor to her, if any of our children were sick

0:06:20.540,0:06:27.700
she should take them there for treatment and he would keep my bill for me.

0:06:27.700,0:06:28.760
She asked me, "Why?"

0:06:28.760,0:06:31.300
From there, trouble started.

0:06:31.300,0:06:35.440
And then... she run outside...

0:06:35.440,0:06:38.920
She held me and fought me.

0:06:38.920,0:06:44.200
She was very big at that time.

0:06:44.200,0:06:46.140
I was struggling with her.

0:06:46.140,0:06:47.800
Imagine if a woman would have beaten me.

0:06:47.800,0:06:53.900
I had to stand on my feet and hit her hard.

0:06:53.900,0:07:02.600
She fell down and when she got up, she broke the windscreen of my car

0:07:02.600,0:07:06.220
in the front and back and then, ran away.

0:07:06.220,0:07:13.560
Obviously, I couldn't control myself so, I took my cutlass.

0:07:13.560,0:07:14.320
Yes.

0:07:14.320,0:07:24.540
She was lucky that I didn't get her; only God knows what would've happened that day.

0:07:24.540,0:07:26.840
After that day, I couldn't take it anymore.

0:07:26.840,0:07:31.040
I told my brother to go and get a large vehicle

0:07:31.040,0:07:35.720
and pack anything she touched inside it and let her take it home

0:07:35.720,0:07:38.540
even though she did not have a dime in my house.

0:07:38.540,0:07:43.100
Anything she touched...

0:07:43.100,0:07:49.560
Then, I took all of my boys and put them in Santana Private Primary School

0:07:49.560,0:07:51.380
where I visited them every two weeks.

0:07:51.380,0:07:58.700
I was a single father; I brought up these children single- handedly.

0:07:58.700,0:08:00.400
Now, anywhere I go...

0:08:00.400,0:08:03.220
I am so emotional.

0:08:03.220,0:08:14.740
Anywhere I went, they were pointing that this was the woman destroying my life.

0:08:14.740,0:08:18.280
Any business I put together, nothing worked.

0:08:18.280,0:08:22.560
The whole thing had affected my children.

0:08:22.560,0:08:28.280
My children, these boys that you see, survived by God's mercy.

0:08:28.280,0:08:41.780
Nobody is a fraudster or thief; they are just good children.

0:08:41.780,0:08:51.200
Imagine a father leaving a country for 22 years and my children were on their own.

0:08:51.200,0:08:53.520
Why should I be happy?

0:08:53.520,0:08:56.220
I had no wife.

0:08:56.220,0:09:03.060
If I married, they ran away and they said it was the same woman who was doing the whole thing - Theresa.

0:09:03.060,0:09:04.300
Look at my granddaughter.

0:09:04.300,0:09:05.440
I had never seen her.

0:09:05.440,0:09:13.880
I only saw her two days ago.

0:09:13.880,0:09:18.000
Look at my other granddaughter.

0:09:18.000,0:09:22.860
She punished me.

0:09:22.860,0:09:29.860
In England, I went everywhere.

0:09:29.860,0:09:33.480
There was no witchdoctor I had not gone to.

0:09:33.480,0:09:39.420
In short, there was nothing else I could do

0:09:39.420,0:09:44.240
until a friend introduced me to The SCOAN.

0:09:44.240,0:09:56.420
My son is a very successful businessman but it is always one step forward and three steps back.

0:09:56.420,0:10:03.600
When he told me, I said that if I returned to Nigeria, I would butcher this woman.

0:10:03.600,0:10:09.740
I would use my cutlass.

0:10:09.740,0:10:17.440
If she didn't die through juju (charms), I would use my cutlass to kill her.

0:10:17.440,0:10:24.540
My son told me that it was better that I come down.

0:10:24.540,0:10:29.300
I told him that I didn't have enough money but he said I should just come.

0:10:29.300,0:10:33.000
He said I should go and check how much a ticket cost.

0:10:33.000,0:10:37.160
I checked the price and before I knew it, he had paid money into my account.

0:10:37.160,0:10:40.440
Without telling anybody, I could not buy anything.

0:10:40.440,0:10:43.220
I wondered what I would do to my children and grandchildren.

0:10:43.220,0:10:46.800
He told me that shopping was not important at this point.

0:10:46.800,0:10:49.720
He had never been to any church.

0:10:49.720,0:10:53.720
If I told him about The SCOAN, he would be laughing at me.

0:10:53.720,0:10:58.180
He told me that he had heard a lot of things about The SCOAN.

0:10:58.180,0:11:03.020
He said that nothing worked and that everyone should defend themselves.

0:11:03.020,0:11:10.420
When I came on the 18th, I came to The SCOAN on Sunday.

0:11:10.420,0:11:14.320
As I sat down there, I couldn't believe my eyes.

0:11:14.320,0:11:27.660
The second person that the man of God touched was me.

0:11:27.660,0:11:31.140
He hit the nail on the head and told me all my problems.

0:11:31.140,0:11:33.420
I had done so many operations.

0:11:33.420,0:11:38.080
I told the doctor concerning my prostate that I would never operate it,

0:11:38.080,0:11:43.320
