0:11:43.320,0:11:48.480
He hit the nail on the head and then told me to bring my whole family

0:11:48.480,0:11:53.960
because there were more things to be revealed.

0:11:53.960,0:12:01.300
I never knew the woman would agree to come to The SCOAN.

0:12:01.300,0:12:05.060
I have two daughters in England, both of them are nurses.

0:12:05.060,0:12:10.480
The oldest one asked me if it was sure that their mother would come.

0:12:10.480,0:12:17.400
I said I didn't know but if she didn't come, I would tell Prophet T.B. Joshua that she is at large

0:12:17.400,0:12:19.500
and he would make her to come.

0:12:19.500,0:12:22.380
That was what I had in mind.

0:12:22.380,0:12:30.060
When I came to Nigeria, I asked my son if he could take me to The SCOAN.

0:12:30.060,0:12:33.180
He said he would give me his driver.

0:12:33.180,0:12:45.100
He gave me his driver and I came to the church early in the morning.

0:12:45.100,0:12:54.620
I told my son what the man of God had said and he said he would follow me.

0:12:54.620,0:12:57.340
This is my oldest son.

0:12:57.340,0:13:00.860
I told him and he agreed.

0:13:00.860,0:13:04.720
My third son is a footballer.

0:13:04.720,0:13:08.160
I tried everything for him to come to England but no way.

0:13:08.160,0:13:09.720
I spent a lot of money but no way.

0:13:09.720,0:13:16.980
He is my third son.

0:13:16.980,0:13:21.620
He doesn't talk to me for no reason.

0:13:21.620,0:13:26.540
He doesn't even talk to his brothers.

0:13:26.540,0:13:32.440
It was from the mum because he was not like this.

0:13:32.440,0:13:45.500
This boy saw me after 22 years at The SCOAN and was smiling at me, peacefully.

0:13:45.500,0:13:46.960
I carried my grandchildren.

0:13:46.960,0:13:49.220
Look at one of them.

0:13:49.220,0:13:52.540
I carried the other one in his hand also.

0:13:52.540,0:13:54.980
This baby was looking at me, smiling.

0:13:54.980,0:14:03.920
She slept in my arms and I wept.

0:14:03.920,0:14:08.640
On Thursday we were here.

0:14:08.640,0:14:21.580
It is a miracle for me to be able to bring them to The SCOAN today for deliverance.

0:14:21.580,0:14:24.040
It is a miracle for me already.

