I want to thank your son, who is not taking sides, he is standing in neutral.

0:16:07.100,0:16:10.860
He believes that he is building his own family.

0:16:10.860,0:16:14.300
Look at the role our brother plays.

0:16:14.300,0:16:25.240
What a role, trying to make sure he is not disconnected from the father or mother.

0:16:25.240,0:16:31.460
If not our brother here, we would not be able to sit here and talk

0:16:31.460,0:16:34.360
because the whole thing would have gone worse.

0:16:34.360,0:16:38.500
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:16:38.500,0:16:49.200
If not the role he played, we would not be here today talking about reconciliation, deliverance, prophecy.

0:16:49.200,0:16:51.300
He made sure he played the role.

0:16:51.300,0:16:55.660
He made sure he invited his father, he even put a money on the account.

0:16:55.660,0:16:59.020
He made sure the father comes, and when the father came...

0:16:59.020,0:17:03.560
He didn't even say no - he said, "Synagogue, OK - let's go".

0:17:03.560,0:17:06.100
He tried to play two roles just like that.

0:17:06.100,0:17:09.500
The youth nowadays - we have a lesson to learn.

0:17:09.500,0:17:12.300
Because normally we take sides.

0:17:12.300,0:17:19.860
Anytime there is trouble between father and mother, instead of you to stand and take a different role...

0:17:19.860,0:17:29.460
I mean to stay clear from this matter and do not disconnect from your mother or father.

0:17:29.460,0:17:35.960
Our role in the matter of our father and mother actually matters.

0:17:35.960,0:17:47.920
If we were able to take a role our brother had taken, the situation would not have come to isolation.

0:17:47.920,0:17:51.940
Make sure to see what you can do by keeping praying for them

0:17:51.940,0:17:54.300
because they are also your father and your mum.

