0:18:25.420,0:18:27.100
So, we still need to ask God.

0:18:27.100,0:18:34.200
We shouldn't be carried away, "the prophet or pastor have said that momma is a witch"- no!

0:18:34.200,0:18:37.900
We still need to ask God.

