0:22:41.320,0:22:43.200
so that someone would be there to take care of the house.

0:22:43.200,0:22:48.440
My dad said he didn't want to see that woman in his territory.

0:22:48.440,0:22:51.240
I didn't use force, I just tried to lure him by saying

0:22:51.240,0:22:57.960
that we should bring my mum to the house for the sake of keeping it clean.

0:22:57.960,0:23:01.000
So, because he listens to me, he agreed to let her come back.

0:23:01.000,0:23:03.520
That's how our mum started staying in our house.

0:23:03.520,0:23:07.920
Each time we came back, she would come to attend to us.

0:23:07.920,0:23:13.380
However, I was a person that didn't believe in miracles.

0:23:13.380,0:23:18.400
My dad told me that if he had money, he wanted to return to Nigeria

0:23:18.400,0:23:22.100
and the first place he would visit is The SCOAN.

0:23:22.100,0:23:27.580
I told him not to believe what he sees on television, that he shouldn't bother.

0:23:27.580,0:23:32.140
However, he insisted that when coming to Nigeria, he would go to The SCOAN.

0:23:32.140,0:23:35.860
I said, OK and asked whether he wanted money for a flight ticket.

0:23:35.860,0:23:40.260
He said that if he had the money, he would enter the next available flight.

0:23:40.260,0:23:43.760
I thought he was joking because I had done so many things to bring him back home

0:23:43.760,0:23:46.640
but each time I raised the topic, he would tell me one story or the other.

0:23:46.640,0:23:51.980
He would make an excuse about kidnapping or poor electricity.

0:23:51.980,0:23:55.400
I told him the electricity should not be a barrier as I had a generator in my house.

0:23:55.400,0:23:57.760
He asked about transportation, that he needed a car to move around.

0:23:57.760,0:24:00.480
I told him not to worry about that as I had cars in my house.

0:24:00.480,0:24:02.560
He kept giving one excuse or another.

0:24:02.560,0:24:08.560
One thing that made him want to come back was because he wanted to visit The SCOAN.

0:24:08.560,0:24:12.200
He said that he was coming back to go to The SCOAN and solve the problem.

0:24:12.200,0:24:15.860
I said that as he had said it; the problem is solved.

0:24:15.860,0:24:20.360
I didn't have the money he was asking for but I had a friend who normally gave him money in England.

0:24:20.360,0:24:22.860
I told him to pay 500 pounds into my dad's account

0:24:22.860,0:24:26.500
because my dad said he had found a ticked for about 500 pounds.

0:24:26.500,0:24:27.860
I told him that I would reimburse him.

0:24:27.860,0:24:32.000
The guy immediately gave him the money and my dad called me that he had received the money.

0:24:32.000,0:24:35.460
The next day, he called me and said the 500 pounds ticket would not work,

0:24:35.460,0:24:38.920
they said it was 625 pounds but I should not worry as he was going to make up

0:24:38.920,0:24:41.900
for the difference; he would get remaining 125 pounds.

0:24:41.900,0:24:47.080
I said to myself, "If daddy is talking like this, then there is a miracle on the way".

0:24:47.080,0:24:50.400
I thought it was a joke until he called me and said he was in Nigeria.

0:24:50.400,0:24:53.160
I didn't believe it.

0:24:53.160,0:24:55.860
I called my elder brother to come to my house so that we could drive

0:24:55.860,0:24:59.300
straight to the airport because I live very close to the airport.

0:24:59.300,0:25:02.520
When my brother came, I told him we were expecting daddy.

0:25:02.520,0:25:04.900
He said, "Yes, but until we see him…"

0:25:04.900,0:25:10.380
We didn't go to the airport until he was outside at arrivals, calling me on the phone.

0:25:10.380,0:25:12.220
We had to rush to go and pick him up.

0:25:12.220,0:25:14.820
Behold, it was our dad!

0:25:14.820,0:25:18.820
I took him home and told everyone that daddy was around.

0:25:18.820,0:25:23.740
The next day he said, "I am going to The SCOAN. Early in the morning, please take me to The SCOAN".

0:25:23.740,0:25:30.720
I told him that I didn't like waking up early in the morning, that I was not a church fan

0:25:30.720,0:25:33.560
and that any of those prophetic things did not work for me.

0:25:33.560,0:25:37.760
My dad said, "You don't want to follow me to The SCOAN and it is very close to your house".

0:25:37.760,0:25:42.240
I told him that I didn't want to go, that I would allow my driver to sleep overnight and take him to The SCOAN.

0:25:42.240,0:25:45.560
So, I asked my driver to sleep overnight and very early in the morning,

0:25:45.560,0:25:47.660
before I had woken up, they had already gone.

0:25:47.660,0:25:56.240
When my dad came back about 1:30 am, he said, "Do you know that the man of God spotted me?"

0:25:56.240,0:25:57.680
He said that he was the second person spotted be the man of God.

0:25:57.680,0:26:01.760
I said, "You? Out of all the congregation and all the people who are coming to The SCOAN,

0:26:01.760,0:26:02.760
the man spotted you?"

0:26:02.760,0:26:03.580
He said, "Yes".

0:26:03.580,0:26:06.400
I told him that I didn't believe him.

0:26:06.400,0:26:08.740
He said, "You didn't watch Emmanuel TV?"

0:26:08.740,0:26:09.940
I said, "I didn't".

0:26:09.940,0:26:14.000
He said, „This man spotted me and the first thing he asked me was, 'Where is your wife?'

0:26:14.000,0:26:16.960
So, this man went directly to the problem”.

0:26:16.960,0:26:18.440
I said, “What?”

0:26:18.440,0:26:24.000
He then said that the man o God said all the family members should come.

0:26:24.000,0:26:26.360
I asked him when the next appointment was.

0:26:26.360,0:26:29.940
He said that he didn’t know whether it was Thursday or Sunday.

0:26:29.940,0:26:32.100
In fact, he was so excited...

0:26:32.100,0:26:34.340
I said, “Let it be Thursday”.

0:26:34.340,0:26:39.460
I was supposed to travel for a job in the east but said that we should gather the whole family.

0:26:39.460,0:26:42.880
He said the first thing he knew was that my mum would not come.

0:26:42.880,0:26:45.020
I said, “Well, let us try that”.

0:26:45.020,0:26:51.700
I called my mother and told her that there was something going on in T.B. Joshua's church,

0:26:51.700,0:26:53.900
very close to where my younger brother lives.

0:26:53.900,0:26:55.680
My mum was staying with my younger brother.

0:26:55.680,0:27:00.640
The perfect thing about this miracle is that my mum who had always been in the village,

0:27:00.640,0:27:07.740
was in Lagos for some months because my younger brother's wife had a baby.

0:27:07.740,0:27:09.680
The whole thing was well arranged.

0:27:09.680,0:27:15.300
I know how I had been trying to get my mum to come and stay in Lagos but she would not want to stay.

0:27:15.300,0:27:18.300
My dad said, “This woman will not come. I bet you she will not come”.

0:27:18.300,0:27:21.600
