0:27:21.600,0:27:27.140
I told my mother that her attention was needed in The SCOAN on Thursday.

0:27:27.140,0:27:28.840
My mum asked, “How early?”

0:27:28.840,0:27:31.280
I told her maybe by 5 am as people were many there.

0:27:31.280,0:27:32.740
My mum said, “No problem”.

0:27:32.740,0:27:36.060
I called my younger brother who she was staying with.

0:27:36.060,0:27:39.600
My younger brother said that he would bring her.

0:27:39.600,0:27:41.460
Nobody complained.

0:27:41.460,0:27:45.340
Very early, around 5 am, we were here and my mum was there.

0:27:45.340,0:27:53.660
Surprisingly, when we went to the canopy, my mum rushed towards my dad for the first time in 34 years

0:27:53.660,0:27:56.980
